body.name: Yaheetech 6-Tier Industrial Style Shoe Rack, Rustic Brown Wood and Black Metal Frame, Holds 24 Pairs of Shoes, 39.5 x 12 x 39.5 Inch
features: 【6-tier Shoe Organizer】This multi-layer storage shoe rack comprises 6 tiers, a top with a drawer, and 5 tiers of mesh shelves of different lengths. The shoes that you often wear in a season can be accommodated. In addition, your keys or some little stuff can be stored in the drawer.
【Optimal Material】Powder-coated iron and CARB P2 MDF board are adopted to craft this multi-layer shoe rack, durable and body-harmless that you can place it in your living or entryway as you need.

【Thoughtful Shelves in Different Lengths】We design the mesh shelves in different lengths. Compared with a moral one with shelves of the same length, such a design allows the shoes with higher bootlegs to be placed more comfortably.

【Adjustable Footpads】Screw-adjustment footpads are adopted, allowing the height of each foot to be changed manually. This multi-layer shoe rack can better adapt to uneven floors and stay stable anywhere.

【Shoe Storage for Entryway】With an overall dimension of 39.5 x 12 x 39.5 inches (L x W x H), this entryway shoe rack is suitable for most of the entryway space. Meanwhile, it can also serve in other rooms to serve as a storage organizer.
body.description: Integrate into the existing style of your space with Yaheetech shoe rack 6-tier entryway shoe rack features a dark rustic wood top with a platform and drawer and a 5-tier metal mesh shelf in different lengths. The mesh shelf adds an airy expression to the storage organizer by reducing the color saturation of the all-black color. The storage shelves in different lengths can be the perfect solution for the arrangement of the shoes with higher bootlegs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Worth every penny
reviews.reviewText: I needed a shoe rack to corral the numerous shoes of the household. I researched and needed it to meet some issues I was having. I needed a multiple size opening for tall boots, needed height to set down coffee cup while putting shoes on/off and also to set items down to turn house alarm off. I needed it to be stylish and sturdy too. This met all those. Very happy with the purchase. My husband made it even sturdier by using some wood glue in the seams when putting it together. It came wrapped nicely too. We’ve had it for a little while now and still very happy with it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 14, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect shoe rack
reviews.reviewText: I can’t speak to the longevity of the rack, as I just got it but it seems really sturdy. All of the pieces were in perfect condition when it arrived, it was easy to put together and it was just what I needed. I think it’s a very good shoe rack for the price, I just wish it came in other colors for the wood.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy and good quality
reviews.reviewText: I fully expected to be disappointed by this shoe rack, but I'm pleasantly surprised at how sturdy it is. It was easy to put together, looks great, and I think it'll last a long time.

reviews.reviewText: This is just what I needed by my door. Holds many pair and is sturdy and love the top shelf and cubby. The instructions need a bit of overhaul though. Good thing I am good at furniture assembly because the directions weren’t good. Love the product though!
